⚠️ Failure Modes (important)
	•	Assuming F = truth
	•	Ignoring tone completely (only using R)
	•	Over-analyzing small Δ
	•	Always blaming self OR always blaming others

👉 Balance is key

⸻

⚡ Final Compression

Most conflict = Δ (felt meaning ≠ literal meaning)

Skill = noticing the gap before reacting

